OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in city centre
OL,4,Cas smoke seen for miles
OL,6,FA large fire has broken out in Swansea
OL,7,Fcity centre, prompting a major
OL,8,Femergency response, road closures and
OL,9,Ftravel disruption across the area.
OL,11,FEmergency services are currently at
OL,12,Fthe scene on Dyfatty Street, near
OL,13,FSwansea railway station, where the
OL,14,Ffire is believed to involve an
OL,15,Findustrial unit.
OL,17,FMid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService said it received the first
OL,19,Freports of the blaze at around 12.30pm
OL,20,Fand crews remain in attendance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
