OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783675170
OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in city centre
OL,4,Cas smoke seen for miles
OL,6,FThick black smoke has been seen
OL,7,Fbillowing from the site and is visible
OL,8,Ffor miles around. Residents living
OL,9,Fnearby have been advised to keep their
OL,10,Fdoors and windows closed while
OL,11,Ffirefighters work to bring the blaze
OL,12,Funder control.
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police have confirmed
OL,15,Fofficers are also at the scene.
OL,17,FDyfatty Street is currently closed
OL,18,Fbetween Orchard Street and Newhall
OL,19,FRoad to allow emergency services to
OL,20,Fdeal with the incident safely.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
