FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783675170
OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in city centre
OL,4,Cas smoke seen for miles
OL,6,FPolice have also warned of heavy smoke
OL,7,Fin the area around the Matthew Street
OL,8,Fflats and are urging motorists and
OL,9,Fpedestrians to avoid the area and use
OL,10,Falternative routes where possible.
OL,12,FThe fire has caused significant
OL,13,Fdisruption across Swansea city centre,
OL,14,Fwith residents describing traffic as
OL,15,F"chaos". Heavy congestion has been
OL,16,Freported on High Street, Bridge Street
OL,17,Fand New Cut Street as drivers divert
OL,18,Faway from the closures.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783675170
OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in city centre
OL,4,Cas smoke seen for miles
OL,6,FThe cause of the fire has not yet been
OL,7,Fconfirmed, and there have been no
OL,8,Freports of any injuries.
OL,10,FWelsh Labour MP for Swansea West,
OL,11,FTorsten Bell, has urged people to stay
OL,12,Faway from the city centre while
OL,13,Femergency services respond to the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FIn a statement, he said: "I'm
OL,17,Fconcerned there may be a large fire in
OL,18,Fcentral Swansea in the city church
OL,19,Farea. I'd recommend staying away until
OL,20,Fit's clear what's going on."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
