PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783675170
OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in city centre
OL,4,Cas smoke seen for miles
OL,6,FIn a separate video, he added: "It's a
OL,7,Fvery significant event. If you are
OL,8,Faround Swansea today, please stay away
OL,9,Ffrom the area around City Church. The
OL,10,Ffire service and the police are fully
OL,11,Fengaged."
OL,13,FEmergency services remain at the
OL,14,Fscene, with further updates expected
OL,15,Fas the situation develops.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
